env.buildCommand:
mkdir $out

cp /nix/store/22k2cj5ciy3mb7y8xhj6l5027sck6kdk-stage-2-init.sh $out/init
substituteInPlace $out/init --subst-var-by systemConfig $out


ln -s /nix/store/a6vxz9zzir71y7hwwg4k0hl9gzyq8qq9-etc/etc $out/etc



ln -s /nix/store/hghy662y18anaqkcdr1vsmjy0bqrzzmi-system-path $out/sw
ln -s "$systemd" $out/systemd

echo -n "systemd 2" > $out/init-interface-version
echo -n "$nixosLabel" > $out/nixos-version
echo -n "x86_64-linux" > $out/system

echo -n "$configurationName" > $out/configuration-name

if [ ! -f /nix/store/16s779f4w8bh6jj3hvmw9my28jh6mgfm-linux-6.6.116/bzImage ]; then
  echo "The bootloader cannot find the proper kernel image."
  echo "(Expecting /nix/store/16s779f4w8bh6jj3hvmw9my28jh6mgfm-linux-6.6.116/bzImage)"
  false
fi

ln -s /nix/store/16s779f4w8bh6jj3hvmw9my28jh6mgfm-linux-6.6.116/bzImage $out/kernel
ln -s /nix/store/nrvnkr9z81pn8c1xnrcfdccmlfbiikrz-linux-6.6.116-modules $out/kernel-modules


echo -n "$kernelParams" > $out/kernel-params

ln -s /nix/store/sy367mv4vsa8prx63jvagk8rbhykfndd-initrd-linux-6.6.116/initrd $out/initrd



ln -s /nix/store/5fazkmakn7xw58vdsvvzm377hna7wmh9-firmware/lib/firmware $out/firmware


mkdir $out/specialisation


(
  source /nix/store/6l9mndwn2z52njn5shabyqc3jr3bxmla-make-shell-wrapper-hook/nix-support/setup-hook

  mkdir $out/bin
  ln -sf /nix/store/48p58ls5qwfpn6qwd0ls61akcr97w4rz-switch-to-configuration-0.1.0/bin/switch-to-configuration $out/bin/switch-to-configuration
  wrapProgram $out/bin/switch-to-configuration \
    --set OUT $out \
    --set TOPLEVEL ${!toplevelVar} \
    --set DISTRO_ID nixos \
    --set INSTALL_BOOTLOADER /nix/store/xik8fwb7mrq7zvlp54qxp97avixv760x-install-grub.sh \
    --set PRE_SWITCH_CHECK /nix/store/pn5f4sck8ff0mdkqn21cl0zqij1r721l-pre-switch-checks/bin/pre-switch-checks \
    --set LOCALE_ARCHIVE /nix/store/9vmxdn26pggj3glazmb68vhcf4smflvz-glibc-locales-2.40-66/lib/locale/locale-archive \
    --set SYSTEMD /nix/store/zf8qy81dsw1vqwgh9p9n2h40s1k0g2l1-systemd-258.2
)

echo "$activationScript" > $out/activate
echo "$dryActivationScript" > $out/dry-activate
substituteInPlace $out/activate --subst-var-by out ${!toplevelVar}
substituteInPlace $out/dry-activate --subst-var-by out ${!toplevelVar}
chmod u+x $out/activate $out/dry-activate
unset activationScript dryActivationScript


cp "$extraDependenciesPath" "$out/extra-dependencies"

/nix/store/qvbwz06cqra3cmlra40v0adw75j6j7wm-jq-1.8.1-bin/bin/jq '."org.nixos.bootspec.v1".toplevel = $toplevel |
."org.nixos.bootspec.v1".init = $init
' --sort-keys --arg toplevel /1rz4g4znpzjwh1xymhjpm42vipw92pr73vdgl6xs1hycac8kf2n9 --arg init /1rz4g4znpzjwh1xymhjpm42vipw92pr73vdgl6xs1hycac8kf2n9/init < /nix/store/brrgj5dvnc26g1x8y44xjn860spqcar9-boot.json | /nix/store/qvbwz06cqra3cmlra40v0adw75j6j7wm-jq-1.8.1-bin/bin/jq --sort-keys '."org.nixos.specialisation.v1" = ($ARGS.named | map_values(. | first))'  > $out/boot.json
